## Section 9 â€” Execution order

Phase 0 â€” Make the backend boundary explicit:
  Add a temporary local/CI denylist script that reports live hits for:
    crate::api, BackendOAuthClient, get_session_token, APP_SESSION_PROVIDER,
    OpenhumanJwt, auth_store_session, backendUrl, apiClient, BACKEND_URL,
    VITE_BACKEND_URL, /auth/me, /agent-integrations/, api.tinyhumans.ai,
    staging-api.tinyhumans.ai, api.openhuman.ai.
  Run it before each phase so regressions are visible.

Phase 1 â€” Direct-only Composio + config default:
  Change `composio.mode` default to direct, migrate/reject backend mode, and remove
  Composio backend client construction. This unblocks IntegrationClient deletion later.
  Run: cargo check --manifest-path Cargo.toml

Phase 2 â€” Delete Tier-1 dead Rust modules and backend inference:
  billing/, referral/, team/ if present on branch, openhuman_backend.rs,
  OpenhumanJwt auth style, cloud embedding defaults.
  Update src/openhuman/mod.rs + src/core/all.rs to remove their wiring.
  Run: cargo check --manifest-path Cargo.toml

Phase 3 â€” Remove backend auth/config/session model:
  app_state local identity, credentials/session_support and backend auth RPCs,
  Config.api_url, config_resolve_api_url, scheduler_gate signed_out,
  doctor/observability/onboarding_status cleanup.
  Run: cargo check + targeted Rust tests

Phase 4 â€” Replace/delete live backend product surfaces:
  webhooks tunnel CRUD, channel managed-DM/send/thread controllers, meet_agent,
  cloud STT/TTS/reply_speech, conscious loop, mascot backend bot, invite/rewards UI.
  Run: cargo check + pnpm compile for touched frontend flows

Phase 5 â€” Delete socket + bus (after moving WebhookRouter):
  Move WebhookRouter to a standalone global in webhooks/.
  Delete src/openhuman/socket/, channels/bus.rs.
  Delete src/api/socket.rs.
  Update event bus startup and registration.
  Run: cargo check

Phase 6 â€” Integration tools and web search:
  Delete/replace Apify, Parallel, Google Places, stock, Twilio, backend web_search,
  and LinkedIn enrichment backend Apify usage. Remove `/agent-integrations/*` tests.
  Run: cargo check + cargo test

Phase 7 â€” Delete remaining src/api/:
  Verify zero callers with: grep -rn "crate::api" src/ | grep -v "^src/api/"
  Then delete the module.
  Run: cargo check + cargo test

Phase 8 â€” Frontend cleanup (Section 4):
  Delete API service files, billing/team/rewards UI, update routes.
  Run: pnpm typecheck + pnpm lint

Phase 9 â€” Config / env / docs / tests (Sections 6â€“8).

Phase 10 â€” Discord native write methods (Section 5.3, non-blocking improvement).

